{"tid":2186360,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮狗實用研報 (壹)：利用投行二世祖分析獲利","createTime":"2020-09-03T02:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T06:15:57.000Z","uid":125976,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"19678050ce63a2084cb978ab284f1c20c755fa88","tid":2186360,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:14:57.000Z","msg":"提到大行報告，大家都話係攞嚟呃散戶信唔過，其實佢哋啲報告係有利用價值，我可以示範一隻 <a href=\"http://1093.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1093.HK&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=b5c9c52f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1093.HK</a> 俾大家睇。<br />\n<br />\n𠵱份係中資行嘅報告，有殘睇字請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>维持&ldquo;买入&rdquo;评级。公司恩必普和肿瘤药维持强劲增长，普药业务有望加速增长，重磅在研品种将陆续上市。维持净利润预测，但考虑到股本扩增，调整公司2020-22 年EPS 预测至0.59/0.70/0.87 元（原0.71/0.84/1/04 元），参考可比公司估值给予公司2020 年35XPE，对应目标价23.20 港元（人民币20.65 元，汇率0.89），维持&ldquo;买入&rdquo;评级。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先無視個目標價，因為我哋唔知道佢有冇用𠵱個價水人。<br />\n<br />\n但係我哋可以假設佢推算過程係正確嘅，即係個預測每股盈利（EPS）係冇水份，只係個 final result 可能有水份。<br />\n<br />\n咁 P/E 細路仔都識計<br />\n<br />\nP/E = Target Price &divide; EPS<br />\nTarget Price = EPS &times; P/E<br />\n<br />\n𠵱個時候去 Aastocks 睇吓個表<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/analysis/company-fundamental/financial-ratios?symbol=01093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fanalysis%2Fcompany-fundamental%2Ffinancial-ratios%3Fsymbol%3D01093&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=f2b55c16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/analysis/company-fundamental/financial-ratios?symbol=01093</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFdeOMi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFdeOMi.jpg&h=f36ed0c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋用加權平均數計吓佢𠵱 5 年，高位 P/E 大約幾多，應該可以得出 35 倍左右，或者你鐘意可以再打個八折。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我哋用二世祖報告 worse case scenario 個 EPS，即係 0.59 RMB<br />\n<br />\n0.59 &times; 35 &divide; 0.9 (RMB to HKD) = HK$22.94<br />\n<br />\n好，結果出咗，仲有 5 蚊水位，夠鐘返工幫二世祖揼垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cf5084273fe3f4a9816c836222dedfd6e4e8c9","tid":2186360,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"𠵱個方法只可以用於有盈利 + 盈利增長穩定嘅股"},{"pid":"384b9b62585425a714837ad788475594c5afa00d","tid":2186360,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:19:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"220a1e938053bc0dd7269550be2f0ee25c99bfa9","tid":2186360,"uid":37919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"出年到$20？"},{"pid":"99703b09771f7894cef212375d4515bae1979659","tid":2186360,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"220a1e938053bc0dd7269550be2f0ee25c99bfa9","tid":2186360,"uid":37919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"出年到$20？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"應該好易到，但我嗰陣係 14 蚊入，均價 12 蚊"},{"pid":"85c4d146422c6067b0a67c769e7a7f4aff629172","tid":2186360,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"而家可以諗吓 1658，業績唔係想象中咁差，只係俾班二世祖洗咗落去，可能係機會"},{"pid":"795d3a860b49620e7b31ab1543a34f2257a5dd29","tid":2186360,"uid":37919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99703b09771f7894cef212375d4515bae1979659","tid":2186360,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"220a1e938053bc0dd7269550be2f0ee25c99bfa9","tid":2186360,"uid":37919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"出年到$20？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"應該好易到，但我嗰陣係 14 蚊入，均價 12 蚊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買隻牛證坐下先"},{"pid":"0469525e4aa06acaf39e9cfe854ce1688c7a0ad4","tid":2186360,"uid":2